{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm speaking about compassion from an Islamic point of view,"},{"time":5000,"text":"and perhaps my faith is not very well thought of"},{"time":8000,"text":"as being one that is grounded in compassion."},{"time":12000,"text":"The truth of the matter is otherwise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"Our holy book, the Koran, consists of 114 chapters,"},{"time":20000,"text":"and each chapter begins with what we call the basmala,"},{"time":24000,"text":"the saying of \"In the name of God, the all compassionate, the all merciful,\""},{"time":30000,"text":"or, as Sir Richard Burton --"},{"time":32000,"text":"not the Richard Burton who was married to Elizabeth Taylor,"},{"time":35000,"text":"but the Sir Richard Burton who lived a century before that"},{"time":38000,"text":"and who was a worldwide traveler"},{"time":40000,"text":"and translator of many works of literature --"},{"time":44000,"text":"translates it. \"In the name of God, the compassionating, the compassionate.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"And in a saying of the Koran, which to Muslims is God speaking to humanity,"},{"time":58000,"text":"God says to his prophet Muhammad --"},{"time":61000,"text":"whom we believe to be the last of a series of prophets,"},{"time":64000,"text":"beginning with Adam, including Noah, including Moses, including Abraham,"},{"time":70000,"text":"including Jesus Christ, and ending with Muhammad --"},{"time":74000,"text":"that, \"We have not sent you, O Muhammad,"},{"time":77000,"text":"except as a 'rahmah,' except as a source of compassion to humanity.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":83000,"text":"For us human beings, and certainly for us as Muslims,"},{"time":87000,"text":"whose mission, and whose purpose in following the path of the prophet"},{"time":92000,"text":"is to make ourselves as much like the prophet."},{"time":96000,"text":"And the prophet, in one of his sayings, said,"},{"time":98000,"text":"\"Adorn yourselves with the attributes of God.\""},{"time":103000,"text":"And because God Himself said that the primary attribute of his is compassion --"},{"time":109000,"text":"in fact, the Koran says that \"God decreed upon himself compassion,\""},{"time":114000,"text":"or, \"reigned himself in by compassion\" --"},{"time":118000,"text":"therefore, our objective and our mission must be to be sources of compassion,"},{"time":125000,"text":"activators of compassion, actors of compassion"},{"time":129000,"text":"and speakers of compassion and doers of compassion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"That is all well and good,"},{"time":136000,"text":"but where do we go wrong,"},{"time":139000,"text":"and what is the source of the lack of compassion in the world?"},{"time":144000,"text":"For the answer to this, we turn to our spiritual path."},{"time":149000,"text":"In every religious tradition, there is the outer path and the inner path,"},{"time":156000,"text":"or the exoteric path and the esoteric path."},{"time":161000,"text":"The esoteric path of Islam is more popularly known as Sufism, or \"tasawwuf\" in Arabic."},{"time":169000,"text":"And these doctors or these masters,"},{"time":172000,"text":"these spiritual masters of the Sufi tradition,"},{"time":176000,"text":"refer to teachings and examples of our prophet"},{"time":180000,"text":"that teach us where the source of our problems lies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184000,"text":"In one of the battles that the prophet waged,"},{"time":188000,"text":"he told his followers, \"We are returning from the lesser war"},{"time":193000,"text":"to the greater war, to the greater battle.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"And they said, \"Messenger of God, we are battle-weary."},{"time":202000,"text":"How can we go to a greater battle?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"He said, \"That is the battle of the self, the battle of the ego.\""},{"time":213000,"text":"The sources of human problems have to do with egotism, \"I.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":222000,"text":"The famous Sufi master Rumi, who is very well known to most of you,"},{"time":228000,"text":"has a story in which he talks of a man who goes to the house of a friend,"},{"time":234000,"text":"and he knocks on the door,"},{"time":237000,"text":"and a voice answers, \"Who's there?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":240000,"text":"\"It's me,\" or, more grammatically correctly, \"It is I,\""},{"time":245000,"text":"as we might say in English."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247000,"text":"The voice says, \"Go away.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"After many years of training, of disciplining, of search and struggle,"},{"time":258000,"text":"he comes back."},{"time":260000,"text":"With much greater humility, he knocks again on the door."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"The voice asks, \"Who is there?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":267000,"text":"He said, \"It is you, O heartbreaker.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"The door swings open, and the voice says,"},{"time":275000,"text":"\"Come in, for there is no room in this house for two I's,\""},{"time":282000,"text":"-- two capital I's, not these eyes -- \"for two egos.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"And Rumi's stories are metaphors for the spiritual path."},{"time":295000,"text":"In the presence of God, there is no room for more than one \"I,\""},{"time":301000,"text":"and that is the \"I\" of divinity."},{"time":306000,"text":"In a teaching -- called a \"hadith qudsi\" in our tradition --"},{"time":310000,"text":"God says that, \"My servant,\" or \"My creature, my human creature,"},{"time":316000,"text":"does not approach me by anything that is dearer to me"},{"time":322000,"text":"than what I have asked them to do.\""},{"time":325000,"text":"And those of you who are employers know exactly what I mean."},{"time":329000,"text":"You want your employees to do what you ask them to do,"},{"time":333000,"text":"and if they've done that, then they can do extra."},{"time":335000,"text":"But don't ignore what you've asked them to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338000,"text":"\"And,\" God says, \"my servant continues to get nearer to me,"},{"time":344000,"text":"by doing more of what I've asked them to do\" --"},{"time":347000,"text":"extra credit, we might call it --"},{"time":349000,"text":"\"until I love him or love her."},{"time":353000,"text":"And when I love my servant,\" God says,"},{"time":356000,"text":"\"I become the eyes by which he or she sees,"},{"time":362000,"text":"the ears by which he or she listens,"},{"time":368000,"text":"the hand by which he or she grasps,"},{"time":373000,"text":"and the foot by which he or she walks,"},{"time":377000,"text":"and the heart by which he or she understands.\""},{"time":382000,"text":"It is this merging of our self with divinity"},{"time":387000,"text":"that is the lesson and purpose of our spiritual path and all of our faith traditions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395000,"text":"Muslims regard Jesus as the master of Sufism,"},{"time":401000,"text":"the greatest prophet and messenger who came to emphasize the spiritual path."},{"time":408000,"text":"When he says, \"I am the spirit, and I am the way,\""},{"time":412000,"text":"and when the prophet Muhammad said, \"Whoever has seen me has seen God,\""},{"time":417000,"text":"it is because they became so much an instrument of God,"},{"time":422000,"text":"they became part of God's team --"},{"time":424000,"text":"so that God's will was manifest through them,"},{"time":428000,"text":"and they were not acting from their own selves and their own egos."},{"time":432000,"text":"Compassion on earth is given, it is in us."},{"time":439000,"text":"All we have to do is to get our egos out of the way,"},{"time":444000,"text":"get our egotism out of the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447000,"text":"I'm sure, probably all of you here, or certainly the very vast majority of you,"},{"time":455000,"text":"have had what you might call a spiritual experience,"},{"time":459000,"text":"a moment in your lives when, for a few seconds, a minute perhaps,"},{"time":466000,"text":"the boundaries of your ego dissolved."},{"time":472000,"text":"And at that minute, you felt at one with the universe --"},{"time":479000,"text":"one with that jug of water, one with every human being,"},{"time":485000,"text":"one with the Creator --"},{"time":489000,"text":"and you felt you were in the presence of power, of awe,"},{"time":494000,"text":"of the deepest love, the deepest sense of compassion and mercy"},{"time":498000,"text":"that you have ever experienced in your lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"That is a moment which is a gift of God to us --"},{"time":508000,"text":"a gift when, for a moment, he lifts that boundary"},{"time":512000,"text":"which makes us insist on \"I, I, I, me, me, me,\""},{"time":518000,"text":"and instead, like the person in Rumi's story,"},{"time":522000,"text":"we say, \"Oh, this is all you."},{"time":528000,"text":"This is all you. And this is all us."},{"time":530000,"text":"And us, and I, and us are all part of you."},{"time":536000,"text":"O, Creator! O, the Objective! The source of our being"},{"time":542000,"text":"and the end of our journey,"},{"time":544000,"text":"you are also the breaker of our hearts."},{"time":549000,"text":"You are the one whom we should all be towards, for whose purpose we live,"},{"time":555000,"text":"and for whose purpose we shall die,"},{"time":559000,"text":"and for whose purpose we shall be resurrected again"},{"time":563000,"text":"to account to God to what extent we have been compassionate beings.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":570000,"text":"Our message today, and our purpose today,"},{"time":574000,"text":"and those of you who are here today,"},{"time":577000,"text":"and the purpose of this charter of compassion, is to remind."},{"time":582000,"text":"For the Koran always urges us to remember, to remind each other,"},{"time":590000,"text":"because the knowledge of truth is within every human being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598000,"text":"We know it all."},{"time":601000,"text":"We have access to it all."},{"time":603000,"text":"Jung may have called it \"the subconscious.\""},{"time":607000,"text":"Through our subconscious, in your dreams --"},{"time":611000,"text":"the Koran calls our state of sleep \"the lesser death,\""},{"time":619000,"text":"\"the temporary death\" --"},{"time":623000,"text":"in our state of sleep we have dreams, we have visions,"},{"time":628000,"text":"we travel even outside of our bodies, for many of us,"},{"time":634000,"text":"and we see wonderful things."},{"time":637000,"text":"We travel beyond the limitations of space as we know it,"},{"time":642000,"text":"and beyond the limitations of time as we know it."},{"time":646000,"text":"But all this is for us to glorify the name of the creator"},{"time":656000,"text":"whose primary name is the compassionating, the compassionate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662000,"text":"God, Bokh, whatever name you want to call him with, Allah, Ram, Om,"},{"time":669000,"text":"whatever the name might be through which you name"},{"time":672000,"text":"or access the presence of divinity,"},{"time":676000,"text":"it is the locus of absolute being,"},{"time":682000,"text":"absolute love and mercy and compassion,"},{"time":686000,"text":"and absolute knowledge and wisdom,"},{"time":689000,"text":"what Hindus call \"satchidananda.\""},{"time":692000,"text":"The language differs,"},{"time":695000,"text":"but the objective is the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":699000,"text":"Rumi has another story"},{"time":701000,"text":"about three men, a Turk, an Arab and --"},{"time":704000,"text":"and I forget the third person, but for my sake, it could be a Malay."},{"time":708000,"text":"One is asking for angur -- one is, say, an Englishman --"},{"time":711000,"text":"one is asking for eneb, and one is asking for grapes."},{"time":716000,"text":"And they have a fight and an argument because"},{"time":719000,"text":"-- \"I want grapes.\" \"I want eneb. \"I want angur.\" --"},{"time":723000,"text":"not knowing that the word that they're using"},{"time":726000,"text":"refers to the same reality in different languages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":729000,"text":"There's only one absolute reality by definition,"},{"time":735000,"text":"one absolute being by definition,"},{"time":738000,"text":"because absolute is, by definition, single,"},{"time":741000,"text":"and absolute and singular."},{"time":744000,"text":"There's this absolute concentration of being,"},{"time":747000,"text":"the absolute concentration of consciousness,"},{"time":750000,"text":"awareness, an absolute locus of compassion and love"},{"time":760000,"text":"that defines the primary attributes of divinity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":764000,"text":"And these should also be"},{"time":767000,"text":"the primary attributes of what it means to be human."},{"time":772000,"text":"For what defines humanity, perhaps biologically,"},{"time":778000,"text":"is our physiology,"},{"time":781000,"text":"but God defines humanity by our spirituality, by our nature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":789000,"text":"And the Koran says, He speaks to the angels and says,"},{"time":793000,"text":"\"When I have finished the formation of Adam from clay,"},{"time":797000,"text":"and breathed into him of my spirit,"},{"time":801000,"text":"then, fall in prostration to him.\""},{"time":805000,"text":"The angels prostrate, not before the human body,"},{"time":813000,"text":"but before the human soul."},{"time":816000,"text":"Why? Because the soul, the human soul,"},{"time":820000,"text":"embodies a piece of the divine breath,"},{"time":826000,"text":"a piece of the divine soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":829000,"text":"This is also expressed in biblical vocabulary"},{"time":834000,"text":"when we are taught that we were created in the divine image."},{"time":840000,"text":"What is the imagery of God?"},{"time":842000,"text":"The imagery of God is absolute being,"},{"time":846000,"text":"absolute awareness and knowledge and wisdom"},{"time":849000,"text":"and absolute compassion and love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852000,"text":"And therefore, for us to be human --"},{"time":856000,"text":"in the greatest sense of what it means to be human,"},{"time":860000,"text":"in the most joyful sense of what it means to be human --"},{"time":863000,"text":"means that we too have to be proper stewards"},{"time":869000,"text":"of the breath of divinity within us,"},{"time":873000,"text":"and seek to perfect within ourselves the attribute of being,"},{"time":878000,"text":"of being alive, of beingness;"},{"time":881000,"text":"the attribute of wisdom, of consciousness, of awareness;"},{"time":886000,"text":"and the attribute of being compassionate and loving beings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":891000,"text":"This is what I understand from my faith tradition,"},{"time":897000,"text":"and this is what I understand from my studies of other faith traditions,"},{"time":904000,"text":"and this is the common platform on which we must all stand,"},{"time":910000,"text":"and when we stand on this platform as such,"},{"time":913000,"text":"I am convinced that we can make a wonderful world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":919000,"text":"And I believe, personally, that we're on the verge"},{"time":925000,"text":"and that, with the presence and help of people like you here,"},{"time":929000,"text":"we can bring about the prophecy of Isaiah."},{"time":935000,"text":"For he foretold of a period"},{"time":939000,"text":"when people shall transform their swords into plowshares"},{"time":946000,"text":"and will not learn war or make war anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":952000,"text":"We have reached a stage in human history that we have no option:"},{"time":958000,"text":"we must, we must lower our egos,"},{"time":967000,"text":"control our egos -- whether it is individual ego, personal ego,"},{"time":972000,"text":"family ego, national ego --"},{"time":978000,"text":"and let all be for the glorification of the one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":983000,"text":"Thank you, and God bless you."},{"time":985000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}